<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧٠٨ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ ,<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{فِي عَيْنٍ حَمِئَةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الكهف: ٨٦]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«حَارَّةٌ»</span> وَكَذَلِكَ قَرَأَهَا الْحَسَنُ عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٧٠٩ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> مَعْمَرٌ وَقَالَ الْكَلْبِيُّ: <span class="c2">«طِينَةٌ سَوْدَاءُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>